Africa's Next Top Model - Season 1, Episode 3




Walk the Walk

After an emotional elimination, the girls were treated to gift bags filled with products from Procter & Gamble. Then, in their first Oluchi Mail, they were told that the remaining 10 girls would be starring in a charity fashion show in Johannesburg the next day, produced by the famed Jan Malan.




Original Air Date: 24-Nov-2013
